snippet.title: Narcosis Trailer 1: "A Taste of Narcosis"
snippet.description: Narcosis is a survival story set at the sunless depths of the Pacific Ocean. Stranded after an accident with little light and few tools, an industrial diver takes desperate steps to surface before his oxygen — and sanity — give out. More info: @narcosisgame and Facebook.com/NarcosisTheGame
